- Yeah, sometimes.

37:24.840 --> 37:26.683
And then sometimes it smells amazing.

37:26.760 --> 37:29.843
It's a study in extremes,

37:29.880 --> 37:32.121
just like everything else in this place.

37:32.280 --> 37:34.009
Mmm!

37:35.160 --> 37:36.241
Can I see the Taj Mahal?

37:36.320 --> 37:38.288
It's about 700 miles away.

37:38.400 --> 37:41.165
- Oh, damn.
